snippet.title: Resident Evil 5: Lost in Nightmares DLC Trailer TRUE-HD QUAITY
snippet.description:
Remember to click the HD button
The first major story pack for Resident Evil 5, Lost in Nightmares pairs RE5 hero Chris Redfield with RE series veteran Jill Valentine for a harrowing lost chapter of the Resident Evil 5 story.
Platforms: Playstation 3 & Xbox 360
Published by: Capcom
Developed by: Capcom
Genre: Third-Person Action 
Release Date:
US: (Lost in Nightmares DLC) February 18, 2010 
Japan: (Lost in Nightmares DLC) Q2/2010 
Europe: (Lost in Nightmares DLC) February 18, 2010 
Australia: (Lost in Nightmares DLC) Q2/2010
